What:		/sys/bus/iio/devices/iio:deviceX/out_altvoltageY_pfd_frequency
KernelVersion:	6.18
Contact:	linux-iio@vger.kernel.org
Description:
		Returns channel Y PFD frequency in Hz, which is the operating frequency
		of the Phase Frequency Detector used in the PLL.

What:		/sys/bus/iio/devices/iio:deviceX/out_altvoltageY_ld_count
KernelVersion:	6.18
Contact:	linux-iio@vger.kernel.org
Description:
		Sets the value for Lock Detector count of a PLL, which determines the
		number of consecutive phase detector cycles that must be within the lock
		detector window before lock is declared. Lower values increase the lock
		detection sensitivity.

What:		/sys/bus/iio/devices/iio:deviceX/out_altvoltageY_ld_count_available
KernelVersion:	6.18
Contact:	linux-iio@vger.kernel.org
Description:
		Returns the available values for the lock dectetor count.